5:
What're you doing?! Fall back or
you'll get hurt!
18: Heheh, see? All according to plan!
23:
You're not fooling anyone.
Can't believe you've made it this far
in life without losing a limb or two.
36:
Something's off... Don't you guys
sense it too?
39:
Lately, whenever we come here, it
feels like we're being watched...
44:
Yeah? I don't smell any danger
though.
49: Neither do I. Are you sure about this?
65:
Yeah.
I swear there's someone staring at
me right now.
69:
It could be some sort of observation
spell... We should stay vigilant.
74:
If you gave us a little more to work
with, we could figure this out.
79:
I'm giving you all I've got, okay? Just
following my instincts here...
84:
Instincts, hm? I suppose it's only
natural to call your extraordinary
power that.
89:
You keep exceeding my
expectations. It's quite vexing.
97:
I don't have any business with the
rest of you. Get out of my sight.
105:
The hole you opened. As annoying
as it is, there's use for it.
109:
You again! What'd you do with Alk
and the others?
113:
Ha, you should be more concerned
about yourself at the moment.
116:
O darkness that lurks within all
creation... Let the shadows inside
spill forth!
122: What kinda weird magic is this?!
126:
Why bother asking about the others
anyway? You have no friends.
129:
Nothing's changed. Nothing will ever
change. You'll always be alone.
137:
You run out before everyone else
because you don't trust them to
watch your back.
140:
You trust no one, and in turn,
nobody ever sticks their neck out for
you. That's just the way your life is.
142:
It's why you want power...
recognition... So you can get
revenge without relying on anyone
else.
147:
That's right, I... I lost everything... so I
have to get stronger on my own...
151:
If it's power you want, then it's right
here... Singularity.
155:
You need but reach out... and hand
me your blade!
165:
If you knew me at all... You'd know
I'm not alone! Not anymore!
168:
I've got a pal out there who taught
me how to move on! You can't
change the past, but you can
change the future!
172:
And I've got a pal who always
believes in me no matter what!
Someone who lets me go wild and
tags along for the ride!
180:
You wanna know why I rush out on
my own all the time?
183:
It's so I can cut a path forward for
my friends, no matter what obstacle
stands in our way!
201:
This is absurd... I just need to...
unleash the darkness within you one
more time!
214:
Haha! Nice going, ripping a hole
through the ceiling with your sword!
218:
Still think you stand a chance? If you
wanna try your luck, then you better
be ready for a pounding!
226:
Hang onto that sword, Singularity...
I'll be back for it one day!
232:
You sure you're okay, Beatrix? You
seem bothered by something.
236: Huh? Nah, I'm perfectly fine! See?
242:
Oh yeah? Then why aren't you
blabbing your head off and
charging ahead on your own?
244:
Which I know you're gonna do.
Because that's who you are.
247:
At the very least, I hope you'll be a
little more careful in the future.
252:
...Haha, are you guys that worried
about me? How sweet!
256:
You can count on me to cut a path
through any foe that gets in our way!
259: So don't lag too far behind, you hear?
